河以外就已經係野外塞外關外不毛之地<br />\n叻嘅咪擸幾個城堡連農地封邑有多啲勢力<br />\n神聖羅馬帝國係掛番以前羅馬帝國嗰名聽落威啲<br />\n其實打飛機架咋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T21:36:33.000Z","msg":"一開始由King of Franks做到羅馬皇帝嘅，實際統治權就係成個East Frank，多數係班強力諸候。係後來Hohenstaufen嘅Friedrich Barbarossa要同教宗周旋，先下放關稅、鑄幣等權力畀諸候。諸候有自己經濟能力，就發展出一個個強藩，所以後尾有個嚟自東方奧地利嘅Habsburg家族，開始收班細諸候皮，再用聯姻蠶食其他強藩。因為球證、旁證、主辦方幾乎都係佢嘅人（教宗除外），所以奧地利之後成日坐正。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea9cdbe764d49d61890968c50467858156650ec2","tid":1000949,"uid":110100,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T21:59:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Nx2CVN0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNx2CVN0.png&h=d2d91bcc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n14-15世紀百年戰爭法國連巴黎都比英國佬搶過<br />\n<br />\n其實德意志民族呢個概念係19世紀先出現，德國統一之前成日狗咬狗骨（三十年戰爭）<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eecd9e144a716968c46ef568fac24d4e264e603","tid":1000949,"uid":61882,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T01:27:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有個嚟自東方奧地利嘅Habsburg家族</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.ausflugsziele.ch/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/1607_museum-ag_habsburg2-800x600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ausflugsziele.ch%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2013%2F02%2F1607_museum-ag_habsburg2-800x600.jpg&h=f56e780d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢個係哈布斯堡<br />\n哈布斯堡家族個名既來源<br />\n呢個<del><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">用下體</span></del>馳騁歐洲幾百年既家族<br />\n其實唔係發源於奧地利<br />\n而係南德既士瓦本地區<br />\n第一個黎自佢地家族既神聖羅馬帝國國王係Rudolf of Habsburg<br />\n係佢將成個家族由士瓦本搬去奧地利<br />\n再係嗰度<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><del>用佢地既下體</del></span>將家族發揚光大<br />\n至於呢個城堡呢<br />\n自十五世紀起就唔係屬於佢地<br />\n咁點解一個咁顯赫既家族會連自己既發源地都保唔住呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原因可以參考番個城堡上面嗰支旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f41a2007e779e063d565237b8d30b555cd02943f","tid":1000949,"uid":45332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2eecd9e144a716968c46ef568fac24d4e264e603","tid":1000949,"uid":61882,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T01:27:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有個嚟自東方奧地利嘅Habsburg家族</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.ausflugsziele.ch/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/1607_museum-ag_habsburg2-800x600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ausflugsziele.ch%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2013%2F02%2F1607_museum-ag_habsburg2-800x600.jpg&h=f56e780d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢個係哈布斯堡<br />\n哈布斯堡家族個名既來源<br />\n呢個<del><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">用下體</span></del>馳騁歐洲幾百年既家族<br />\n其實唔係發源於奧地利<br />\n而係南德既士瓦本地區<br />\n第一個黎自佢地家族既神聖羅馬帝國國王係Rudolf of Habsburg<br />\n係佢將成個家族由士瓦本搬去奧地利<br />\n再係嗰度<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><del>用佢地既下體</del></span>將家族發揚光大<br />\n至於呢個城堡呢<br />\n自十五世紀起就唔係屬於佢地<br />\n咁點解一個咁顯赫既家族會連自己既發源地都保唔住呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原因可以參考番個城堡上面嗰支旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T01:32:59.000Z","msg":"瑞士<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac428e5e9d89884554fd0ab2b4581ccfc3e49e14","tid":1000949,"uid":49549,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T01:36:39.000Z","msg":"既非神聖 亦不羅馬 更不是帝國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04bb7dd82d3daee91c12dadfd37c5e3d62095267","tid":1000949,"uid":51920,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T01:41:04.000Z","msg":"查理曼"},{"pid":"ec9d0ee89cbbcf2c5d265abf7ff262036d678895","tid":1000949,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T02:20:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/norma